<section sectnbr = "1J">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "10">
<configtype typenbr = "1">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "S8T40A1A16003" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Water Pump and Generator Drive Belt Removal and Installation (M16A)
</title>
<servinfosub id = "S8T40A1A16003001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect negative cable at battery.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
If vehicle equipped with A&#x002F;C, remove compressor drive belt before removing water pump belt (1).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Refer to 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A6306008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Loosen drive belt adjusting bolt (2) and generator pivot bolt (3).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5JB0A1A0001.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "55.742mm" ver = "01" gw = "156" gh = "141"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Loosen water pump and generator drive belt adjuster bolt (4) to displace generator and then remove water pump belt.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "S8T40A1A16003002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install belt (1) to water pump pulley (2), crankshaft pulley (3) and generator pulley (4).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Adjust belt tension by referring to 
<intxref refid = "S8T40A1A16004">Water Pump and Generator Drive Belt Tension Inspection and Adjustment (M16A):M16A and J20A</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
If vehicle equipped with A&#x002F;C, install compressor drive belt referring to 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A6306008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5JB0A1A0002.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "56.447mm" ver = "01" gw = "172" gh = "143"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect negative cable at battery.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
